# The Network & Routing Architecture — Cross-Concern Guardrails

> **Companion document** to:
> - `04-http-alova.mdc` — HTTP client rules (Alova ONLY, builder patterns, useHttpRequest)
> - `08-router-rbac.mdc` — Router & RBAC rules (DynamicRouteManager, meta contract, v-auth)
> - `04-state-boundaries.mdc` — Data flow isolation (api → hooks → stores → views)
>
> This document covers the **gaps between those rules**: cross-layer interactions, error responsibility, type-safety anti-patterns, and operational patterns that AI agents commonly hallucinate.

---

## §1 — HTTP ↔ Router Cross-Layer Interaction Contract

HTTP 层和 Router 层通过 **依赖注入 (DI)** 交互，**绝不**通过直接 import。

### The DI Bridge

`src/infra/auth/tokenProvider.ts` 提供两个注入点：

```ts
// 应用入口 (main.ts / plugin) 注入 —— 唯一合法的接线点
import { setTokenProvider, setOnUnauthorized } from '@/infra/auth/tokenProvider'

setTokenProvider(() => userStore.token)          // HTTP 层通过 getToken() 读取
setOnUnauthorized(() => userStore.logout())       // 401 最终回调
```

### 401 → Logout → Login 完整链路

```
Interceptor 检测 401
  → TokenRefreshCoordinator.acquireFreshToken()
    → 刷新成功 → 自动重发排队请求
    → 刷新失败 → triggerUnauthorized()
      → 注入的回调 (userStore.logout()) 清除 token / 重置 stores
        → 下一次导航时 beforeEach 检测 isLogin === false
          → redirect → /login?redirect=...
```

**关键事实**: Pinia store `logout()` 绝不调用 `router.push('/login')`。重定向由 permission guard 自动完成。

### FORBIDDEN — 跨层违规

| FORBIDDEN | WHY | CORRECT |
|-----------|-----|---------|
| `import { useUserStore } from '...'` inside `interceptors.ts` | HTTP 层不得依赖 Pinia | `getToken()` / `triggerUnauthorized()` from `@/infra/auth/tokenProvider` |
| `router.push('/login')` inside interceptor catch block | HTTP 层不得依赖 vue-router | `triggerUnauthorized()` 触发 logout；guard 自动重定向 |
| `if (res.status === 401) { userStore.logout() }` in business code | 401 由 `TokenRefreshCoordinator` 独占处理 | 什么都不做；拦截器静默处理 |
| `import router from '@/router'` inside Pinia store | Store 不得依赖 vue-router | 如需路由信息用 `@/infra/router/routeProvider` |

