| 4 | Error UI | `watch(error, e => $message.danger(e.message))` | 拦截器已弹通知；仅处理领域错误 | §2 |
| 5 | 401 Auth | `if (res.status === 401) { logout() }` | `TokenRefreshCoordinator` 自动处理 | `04-http-alova` R4 |
| 6 | Auth DI | HTTP 层 `import { useUserStore }` | `getToken()` / `triggerUnauthorized()` from tokenProvider | §1 |
| 7 | DTO Typing | `get('/api/users')` 无泛型 | `get<UserListRes>('/api/users')` | §3 |
| 8 | DTO Typing | `interface Res { data: any }` | 命名 DTO + 具体类型 | §3 |
| 9 | DTO Location | DTO 定义在组件或 Store 中 | `src/types/dto/` 或 `src/api/<module>/` | §3 |
| 10 | Route Import | `import View from '@/views/...'` 同步 | `() => import('@/views/...')` 懒加载 | §4 |
| 11 | Navigation | `router.push({ path: '/system/user' })` | `goToRoute('SystemUser')` | `08-router-rbac` R3 |
| 12 | Navigation | `router.push('/dashboard')` 硬编码 | `goToRoute('Dashboard')` 按 name | §5 |
| 13 | Route Reg | `router.addRoute()` / `router.removeRoute()` | `DynamicRouteManager.addRoute()` | `08-router-rbac` R1 |
| 14 | Store↔Router | Pinia store 中 `import router from '@/router'` | `@/infra/router/routeProvider` 只读路由信息 | `04-state-boundaries` |
| 15 | Store↔API | Pinia action 中 `requestXxx()` | composable 编排：`api → hook → store → view` | `04-state-boundaries` |
| 16 | Connection | `window.addEventListener('online', ...)` | `addConnectionListener()` from connection.ts | §6 |
| 17 | Connection | `if (!navigator.onLine)` 散落检查 | `getConnectionState().isConnected` | §6 |
| 18 | Upload | 手动 `new FormData()` + `post()` | `uploadFile()` / `uploadFiles()` | §8 |
| 19 | Download | `fetch().then(r => r.blob())` | `downloadFile()` | §8 |
| 20 | Retry | 非幂等 POST 设置 `retry.retries > 0` | 仅重试幂等请求 (GET/HEAD) | §7 |
| 21 | Silent Error | 后台轮询不使用 `globalError: 'silent'` | 后台/探测请求设置 `globalError: 'silent'` | §2 |

