## §10 — Pre-Output Self-Verification Checklist

在生成任何 HTTP 或 Router 代码之前，心理执行以下检查：

- [ ] No `axios` / `fetch` / `XMLHttpRequest` — 仅 `@/utils/http/methods` 或 `useHttpRequest`
- [ ] No redundant toast/message for errors — 拦截器已处理全局错误通知
- [ ] No 401/token handling in business code — `TokenRefreshCoordinator` 独占处理
- [ ] No `any` on API response types — 所有响应用 DTO 完整定义类型
- [ ] No synchronous view imports in routes — 全部使用 `() => import(...)`
- [ ] No hardcoded path strings — 使用路由 name + `goToRoute()`
- [ ] No direct `router.addRoute()` — 使用 `DynamicRouteManager`
- [ ] No Pinia store importing `vue-router` or `src/api/`
- [ ] File uploads use `uploadFile()` / `uploadFiles()`
- [ ] File downloads use `downloadFile()`
- [ ] Background/polling requests use `globalError: 'silent'`
- [ ] Non-idempotent requests (POST/PUT/DELETE) have `retry.retries = 0`
